title: Application Event Logs
extract: 1) Open Event Viewer, Then Click Event Viewer. 2) In Event Viewer, in the console tree, click Application. (In the details pane, make sure that there are no errors reported in the application event log that indicate the restore was unsuccessful).May 26, 2017
